description: Mistress Kara is back on the US mats. She is Currently Undefeated. She missed competing for the welter weight belt last season due to an injury but she's back and stronger than ever. Cheyenne Jewel has pumped up to welter weight this season and all that extra weight as gone straight to her beautiful ass. She used her weight well against Penny Barber for an easy win. Today she faces the biggest, stronger wrestler on the roster, Mistress Kara.
title: Mistress Kara is Back and After the Belt, Cheyenne Jewel stands in her way
